Dialogs.Dialog: All right, today I'll go all out becoming a library committee！ Yeah！
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
So you didn't quit the library committee.
What are you saying all of the sudden？
...Hey.
Hm？
It's distracting when you space out like that.
I'm a bit bored... Anything interesting that can be read fast？
The elementary school's assigned books.
Oh, so you have those here.
In the children's library.
Hey, can't you be a bit livelier？
I can't. Besides, I have my fun reading books.
I think I'll read some books too. Any recommendations？
Oh, so you have those... Hey, did this conversation just loop？
It did.
(What should I say...？)
All right, today I'll go all out becoming a library committee...
Well, I'm pretty bored...
Rinko
Aren't you gonna answer？
*sigh*...
What？
...Just the 3 of you can go. This way we won't have to worry about each other, you know.
...Listen, you really don't need to worry. I'm fine on my own. Bye.
Is it okay？ If you have somewhere to go, well...
Oh, shut up！
Hey！
▲小早川＊▲, is late... We're gonna need to close the library soon.
Where did ▲小早川＊▲ go？
*Sniff*... *Sniff*...
！？... Someone's crying？
...What is it？
Oh, I was thinking we should probably close up soon. You've got the key, right？
Yeah.
...Hey, just now...
You can go now. I'll close the door before leaving.
(▲小早川＊▲... She was crying, wasn't she？)
(It's getting kinda late...)
Rinko
Geez, you're annoying！
(！？ That's... ▲小早川＊▲, isn't it？)
Rowdy
I'm tellin' ya to wait！
(And with her, a dangerous-looking guy...)
！！ Good timing！
Who the heck are ya？ Her boyfriend？
Yeah. We're on a date right now.
Huh！？ R-Really？
Of course！ And this guy is super strong.
"This" guy？ ... Who？
It's you, of course！ Beat him up good！
Oh... Kid, so you're gonna beat me up good？
Well, beat up, huh...
Come on, bring it！！
▲小早川＊▲, run！
Eh？
So... To sum things up, you were playing a fighting game at the arcade, then he challenged you.
Rinko
Yeah.
Then he lost pretty badly against you, and got angry.
Right.
So, ▲小早川＊▲ what did you do？
I kicked him.
Don't just kick people！
He was persistent！ It was self-defense. Plus, I'm a weak girl. You should've fought instead of running away. Aren't you a man？
What if the police came then？
Yeah, now I feel so annoyed...
If I lost, what would happen to ▲小早川＊▲？
You were just scared.
Right？ You should've beaten him up. Well, you're a man, after all.
Oh, sounds like something someone older than me would say.
Well, I guess I'll thank you for now.
Yeah, yeah... So, what are we gonna do after this？
I'll tell you something. That date thing earlier, that was just something I said on the spot to...
Nah... I mean it's late, so I should probably accompany you home. That guy might still be around.
Oh, yeah. Well, I guess that's okay...
Say...
You know, you could've just fled on your own and left me there.
Why didn't you do so？
Why？ Well... It just happened.
Hmm...
...It's here.
Okay. See you later, then.
Yeah.
All right, today I'll go all out being a library committee！
Oh！
Hey, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Hello.
(Work's done for today. Now all I have to do is to wait for closing time, as usual...)
(▲小早川＊▲ is the same as always... It's like that incident the other night was a lie.)
(She's cute when she's calm like this... Her eyes are big, her eyebrows are long, and her cheeks are...)
Hey.
Whoa！ No, I'm sorry！！
...What？！ Were you thinking of something indecent？
No way！ ...So, what is it？
Today, I'll go to the arcade after school.
Oh. But, huh...？ Won't you see that guy again？
Yeah, that's the thing.
Hah... I think I'll let you go for now！
▲小早川＊▲... I had no idea you were so good. At fighting games, especially.
Well, sort of. I come over here pretty often.
If you want to be my opponent, you're gonna have to hone your skills, okay？
Sorry... So, shouldn't we be heading home？ Shall I accompany you？
Huh？ Well... No need for today.
Well, it's pretty late already, isn't it？
Stop acting so grown up already. Bye！
Oh, hey！
(There she goes... Is she gonna be okay？)
All right, I should be going to bed.
... But I'm kind of hungry. I'll go to the convenience store！
(Where are the mackerel cans...？ Oh, there. I'll give myself a treat and buy the gold label！ )
Rinko
There are actually high school students buying mackerel cans at night...
So, what are you doing in a place like this？
Well, I was hungry, so I came to buy something. I live pretty close.
And you're going for mackerel？ You're not a salary man.
Why not？ There's DHA in it. And what are you doing, ▲小早川＊▲？
Huh... I was taking a walk, and here I am.
This is no time for a walk... You're still in your uniform, too.
Who cares？ How about you just go home and go to bed？
You too, ▲小早川＊▲. I'll accompany you home.
Leave me alone, you nosy old man.
I'm just a year older！ ...And there's no way I can leave you alone outside, at this hour.
Hey, wait！
Clerk
Hey, mister！ Your bill！
Huh！？ Oh, yeah... ▲小早川＊▲！
Thank you very much.
(I lost sight of her... I wonder if ▲小早川＊▲ will be okay...)
All right, today I'll go all out being a library committee！
(▲小早川＊▲'s not here... Nothing could've happened to her, right？)
▲小早川＊▲！ How come you're here at this hour？ And in private clothes？
Rinko
No reason.
(So she doesn't want to stay home, or... She was in her uniform at the store last time we met...)
(It probably has something to do with her crying on the roof...)
(But for her to go through the trouble of coming here now... Is it possible that she's counting on me...？)
(...Am I thinking too much？ But, I should... All right！)
Say, are you free on next Sunday？
...Why？
Well, um... I was thinking about a date.
D-Date... Who？ With whom？
▲小早川＊▲ and... I-
...What are you saying？ That's just stupid...
I-I see... Well, I guess so.
...Sunday, you said？
Yeah.
I can go with you... I guess.
Really？
But it's not a date or anything！ It's just... normal hanging out.
Sure. Then we'll be just hanging out.
Hah... Isn't the warmth of spring nice？
Rinko
To old people, surely.
I'm just one year older... So, let's get on with our da...
Da... Day together. Say, can't you act a bit happier？
Nope.
Okay... But, it feels nice outside！
Yeah... This place hasn't changed at all.
You used to come here often？
When I was a kid, we'd come here often, all 3 with a lunch box... Let's go over there, okay？
Say... I might be barging in, but is there something wrong...？
Not really.
I see... It's okay if you don't wanna talk about it.
Today... My new mother and little brother were visiting.
New mother and brother, you mean...
My father is remarrying. It's complicated. Got it？
Shouldn't you have stayed home, then？
You don't get it... If you're a nuisance, you get out. That's how it works.
Everyone gets depressed when I'm around.
So I'm just killing time right now. Satisfied？
I'm not getting depressed
Is there something I can do？
Okay, I'm satisfied
So, it's not everyone at all.
I'm so nosy anyway, right？
For now, I'm glad I could hear what was going on.
See you later. Go straight home, all right？
If you don't promise me, I'll walk you...
I'll go home！
Good... I'm always free to talk. Let's have another da... uh... day out, okay？
Nosy old man...
Just older by a year, though！
(I really think I should've walked her home...)
Wow！ It's blazing out here！
Rinko
What are you all worked up about...？
Because it's a date... Hey, ▲小早川＊▲, are you all right？
I'm not all right, and this isn't a date...
...Uh, let's get under the shade, okay？ Maybe next to that family.
No.
It's just...
Not next to them. No way.
Okay.
I'm going to die out here. Let's get some ice cream...
Oh... Hey！
Feeling cooler now？ Sorry for making you come out here with me.
It's fine. I don't want to stay home, anyway.
I've been watching, and... Is something bugging you？
Not really... Just my new mother and brother.
New mother and brother, you mean...
My dad's getting remarried. That's all.
I see... Maybe you really should be at home, then...
When you're in the way, move it. That's what I'm good at.
Plus, I'm the one who dragged you along. So, thank you. Is this good enough？
I'm not being "dragged along"
It's not good at all！
Yeah, guess so
I just wanted to have a chance to talk with ▲小早川＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲, how can you be all right with that？
I wanted to have a chance to talk with you.
Bye. Go straight home, okay？
If you don't promise, I'll walk you there.
I'll go home！
Good. I'm always free to talk, okay？ Let's have another da-... day together.
Nosy old man...
Just older by a year, though！
(I really think I should've walked her home...)
When you're talking about a date, it's gotta be the zoo！
Rinko
They are beasts... Also, you said a "date"？
You must've heard wrong. Now, ▲小早川＊▲, what do you wanna see？
There's nothing I wanna see.
Hey... There's gotta be something, right？ Like elephants, or giraffes...
No. Big animals scare me.
Well, what about rabbits？
Their eyes scare me.
Huh, then...
I'll go see the ocelots.
The what？... Hey, wait！
You look like you've been here often... We've only seen felines, though.
Sort of. When I was a kid, the three of us would come here often and...
...And？
Nothing...
I was wondering... Did something happen today？
Nothing... Just, I have a new mother and little brother coming home.
New mother and brother, you mean...
My father is remarrying. It's obvious if you think about it, geez.
I see... So because of that, you decided to...
That's why I came here. Everyone gets depressed when I'm around.
If you're a nuisance, you get out. Don't you get it？
I'm not getting depressed
Don't say you're a nuisance
Yeah, I got it
So, it's not everyone at all, right？
That's just weird！
And you're okay with that, ▲小早川＊▲？
See you later. Go straight home, okay？
If you don't promise me, I'll walk you home.
I'll go home！
Good... I can listen to your problems anytime. So, let's have another da... uh... day out, okay？
Nosy old man...
Just older by a year, though！
(I really think I should've walked her home...)
I thought the beach was a nice idea, but when I really got here... Brrr！
Rinko
Really？ I think it feels great！
R-Really？ We can go somewhere else, if you want？
I like it here！
Oh... Okay...
The beach in the winter is nice. Less crowded.
Well, that's true. Because it's freezing.
Geez... Well, why don't you go home！？
I can't just up and leave during a date...
Hm？ Did you say "date"？
Just your imagination...
I'm gonna find a crab！
The wind's dying down. Much better...
The years were hard on you, huh？
Not "years," just one. Still, today was fun.
I was just thinking it was a good idea to invite you, you know？
...Today, my new mother and little brother are showing up.
New mother and brother, you mean...
My dad's getting remarried. It's a little weird right now. That's all.
Maybe I shouldn't have asked you to come here...
I would have just found some place to kill time. I'm just in the way.
Thanks to you, they could have a good time today, too.
Is that really okay？
Don't say it like that！
I guess it worked out, then
I'm sure that nobody feels that way...
It's not true！ Okay？
If everybody's happy, then that's okay, huh？
See you later. Go straight home, okay？
If you don't promise me, I'll walk you home.
I'll go home！
Good... I can listen to your problems anytime. So, let's have another da... uh... day out, okay？
Nosy old man...
Just older by a year, though！
(I really think I should've walked her home...)
It's this late already... Time to go to bed！
...Or so I thought. But ▲小早川＊▲'s usually at the convenience store at this hour... I'm a bit worried.
And my stomach's growling, too. I guess I'll go.
Rinko
Ah...
Hah, I knew it！... Why is it that you're here again, at this late hour？
What about you？ They sell mackerel cans everywhere, you know.
I can only find the gold label here！ ...So, what are you doing？
It's none of your business. How about you buy that can and go home？
You too, ▲小早川＊▲. I'll walk you home.
No. I'm staying here.
You can't do that.
Leave me alone！ Go away！
Hey, I've got a question.
You're really forceful. You know that？
Sort of. I also have a question.
...What？
Is it hard for you to stay at home？ You stayed out the whole time since school, did you？
So what？ I'm free to do that if I want.
I'm free to be worried if I want, too.
If you feel like talking about it, I'll listen.
...I'm okay from here.
Okay. It's a good thing we didn't get caught by the police. We are minors, after all.
Well, good night.
Nah, forget it... Make sure you don't get caught on your way back.
(She's right... I'd better hurry home！)
Hey, ▲小早川＊▲. That book you're reading, what's it about？
Rinko
... You wouldn't understand even if I told you.
Now, now. Don't be like that. What's it about？
Hah... It's about a world where all the people except the main character and his little sister are just some retards.
That's extreme...
That's why I told you that you wouldn't understand.
So you understand it, ▲小早川＊▲？
I understand. I don't need anyone, really. I'd rather be on my own.
How come？
Because everyone's an enemy, in my world.
Enemy... That can't be true？
It is true. I'm a nuisance wherever I go.
It's the same at school. Everyone's an enemy.
It must be hard... having this kind of mindset.
I'm okay. It's perfect. The world VS. Rinko... It's pretty exciting.
...Why would someone who's okay cry then？
！！ ...Nobody's crying.
You were crying. On the roof...
I wasn't！... I'm going home.
It's this late already... Time to go to bed！
Huh？ It's from ▲小早川＊▲...
"They started selling Premium Gold mackerel cans. - Rinko."
Oh, Premium Gold... But why did she e-mail me at this late hour...？ Ah！！
Hah, hah... ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
This is the Premium Gold, you know.
Did anything happen？
...Not really.
Not really what！？ Then why are you...
Clerk
Excuse me... You're disturbing the other customers...
Huh？ Oh, sorry...
Say, are you angry？
I'm not. But you had some business with me, right？
Yeah... Wanna go somewhere next Sunday？
Oh, sure.
Okay... That was all.
No way... You went through the trouble just to ask me that？
Well, I didn't want to wake you up with a phone call, if you were sleeping...
Just wake me up then！ What if I hadn't seen that mail！？
You are angry, after all...
I'm not angry. Just... don't be unreasonable...
Um...
Thank you.
Sure. See you later.
(So, she still doesn't like to be home...)
Yes, the amusement park！ An ideal spot for a da...
Rinko
"Da"？
...So！ Where do we go？
There！ That one over there！
Hey, don't run！
For a ride, those coffee cups were spinning way too fast. Geez...
Don't go acting like an old man. Since we are here, why don't we just have fun？
Well, I guess. Say...
Hmm？
Were they over today too？ I mean... Your new mother and little brother.
Yeah...
So you hate her that much... Does she treat you badly or something？
No way... She's a really nice woman. It looks like she really loves my good-for-nothing father, too...
She's really worried about Rinko, too.
The one who's wrong is always Rinko...
Then, at least...
I can't. I can't bring myself to smile in front of them.
Mama... My real Mama, who gave birth to me... I feel so sad for her.
Hey, about your world you were talking about.
...Huh？
You can have an ally in that world, right？ Then, I'll be that ally.
So... don't go crying on your own. Okay？
...Okay.
Can I tell you one thing？
What is it？
You really love to butt into people's problems, don't you？ Like some guardian or something.
I also feel like I've gotten myself an unreasonable little sister, sometimes...
Oh, so would you like it if I called you... "Big Brother"？
Big Brother！？
I really like it！
Nah...
Well, that's... Isn't that something quite embarrassing...？
I'm not gonna call you that.
Ah, okay.
Big Brother, eh？ I think that's good. Yeah.
You like it？ I see, I see...
...Lolicon！
(I saw that coming...)
Nah. I think I'll pass.
What？ Why not！？ You're no fun, Big Brother！
(I'm being teased...)
I wonder if it's better that you talk to your family. Maybe there's a way to solve the problem.
Okay, got it. Say...？
Ever since Rinko was born, today was Rinko's first date... That's all. See you later.
Oh, okay... Bye...
(That made me blush a little...)
Well, I guess I'll be heading off to bed now...
Hmm？ It's from ▲小早川＊▲...
"Aren't you gonna buy a mackerel can tonight？ I'll be waiting. - Rinko."
Now, at such an hour... Did something happen？
Hah, hah... ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Hehe... So you came to see me.
Did... something happen？
Sorry to have made you worry. It's okay. I told them I'd come back soon.
But, you're still out at this late hour...
This will be the last time. I just wanted to report to you as soon as I could...
Oh... So, you were able to tell them about your feelings？
Yeah. "You don't have to smile, but let's try living all together," they said... That made me cry.
Looks like your father and new mother are really nice people.
They are. They make me feel like I'm still a little kid.
Thanks. I'll be okay here.
So, no more night walks？
Hehe... Will you get a little lonely？
A little. But we'll see each other again pretty soon.
Yeah. That's true... You know, the way you're acting, it makes me feel...
Sorry. Excuse me.
Hello？ Yeah, I'm okay. I'm right in front... Yes, yes. Bye.
From your parents？
Yeah. They told me to come home quickly.
I see. Well then, good night.
Good night！
I am curious about what she said... I made her feel what...
Excuse me！ I came to return the key to the library.
Teacher
Oh, you. Good timing.
Yes？
Sorry, but could you help me copy these？ It'll take about 10 minutes.
Well, sure.
Geez, that wasn't 10 minutes at all... It's almost evening. Eh？
▲小早川＊▲, I thought you had gone home already... Have you been waiting for me？
Rinko
No！... I just... I was sort of thinking about something, and it became this late...
Thinking about something？ At the school gate？
That happens sometimes, right...？
Huh... Does it？
Now, now. Who cares about the details. Let's go！
That's weird. I feel like it's the first time I walk you home at a decent hour.
Hehe, that might be true. Thanks.
Well, see you later.
Okay... Say, it is nice to have someone saying "see you later" to you, right？
It is. It'd be good if you can make more friends and say that to them.
Yeah... But you know... For Rinko, it's okay to have just one person for now.
Nothing... See you later！
Ah, see you later！
Oh, it's already this time...
Rinko
Hey, hey. How about going to the arcade on the way home？
You really like it, huh？ Well, I'll join you！
We are here！ Well, which one am I going to beat the crap out of today？ Ah...
Hey, let's go home. That guy is here...
Hah... I see. ▲小早川＊▲, you go home first.
Why？... Wait. What do you think you're doing！？
Rowdy
Oh, it's you from before！
Yes. Say... If I let you hit me once, will it make us even？
Oh？ What a brave heart？ Let's take it outside then.
He punched me twice... Ouch...
Hey, I don't get it at all！ Are you a masochist？
That's why I told you to go home first. This is so uncool...
It's not the time to be cool！ What if you get serious injuries？
But you like to go to that arcade, don't you？ Now you don't have to worry about that guy anymore.
That's... That's the reason you got in a fight...？
Thanks for walking me home. There's nothing to worry about. I'm fine.
Don't try to show off！ But...
I think you were so cool. If I had an older brother, I wish he would be just like you. Really.
Hahaha... It would be troublesome to have such a violent sister then.
...Rinko is not your sister！
Huh？... I know that.
Yes, it's good that you know... Bye. See you later！
(？？ What was that...？)
Oh, it's already this time.
Rinko
Hey, hey. How about going to the arcade on the way home？
You really like it, huh？ Well, I'll join you！
We are here！ Well, which one am I going to beat the crap out of today？ Ah...
Hey, let's go home. That guy is here...
...▲小早川＊▲, you go home now.
Why？... Wait. What do you think you're doing！？
Hey, you want a piece of me？
Rowdy
You, from before... How courageous. Let's take it outside！！
I was no match for him... Ouch...
You could never win against such a big guy！ Are you an idiot or just simply crazy！？
Don't keep saying I'm an idiot. It hurts.
You are just so weak. What if that store clerk didn't call the police？
But that guy wouldn't be able to come to the arcade for a while, right？ This way, you can enjoy your time there.
That's... That's the reason you... You idiot...
I didn't get any serious injury. You didn't have to worry.
Nah, it's good to have Rinko walk you home every once in a while, right？
Well, thank you. Go home carefully, okay？
...Say. I got one question.
You said before that Rinko was like your little sister, right？
But Rinko didn't think that way at all...
Sorry. That was just a joke.
I didn't mean that... Never mind. You idiot！
(How many times did she call me "idiot" today...？)
Oh, it's already this time...
Rinko
Hey, hey. How about going to the arcade on the way home？
You really like it, huh？ Well, I'll join you！
We are here！ Well, which one am I going to beat the crap out of today？ Ah...
Hey, let's go home. That guy is here...
Oh my... This can't be helped, huh？ ▲小早川＊▲, you go home first.
... Wait. What do you think you're doing！？
Excuse me. Got a minute？
Rowdy
Oh, you from before！
Yes. Um... I have to apologize that my girlfriend kicked you.
If apologizing works, why do we need the police, hah！？
Right... So that's what you have to say... *sigh*
Ouch... I didn't plan for this at all...
You okay...？ I don't think so.
That gorilla wouldn't accept any apology. You should've known.
Well, he let me go in the end. He didn't kick me badly either. Hey, am I like a big brother now？
Yeah. Thanks...
I'm okay here. Thanks for walking me！
But, it's all because of Rinko...
It's not a big deal, so don't worry. It's unavoidable when I have such a violent little sister like you, huh？
Hey... I'm not your sister.
It was a joke.
It's not a joke for me. I mean, I don't want to be your sister...
Never mind！ Hehe. See you later！
Ah... Bye...
